1. Clone verlihub.git repository

2. git clone git://github.com/shurshur/vh_perl.git /path/to/verlihub.git/verlihub/plugins/perl

3. cd /path/to/verlihub.git/verlihub/plugins

4. patch -p2 < perl/vh-cmake.patch

5. cd perl

6. cmake ../.. && make && make install

7. cd vh

8. perl Makefile.PL && make && make install

9. Type in hub mainchat: !addplug perl -p /path/to/libperl_pi.so -d "Support for perl scripts"

10. Type in hub mainchat: !onplug perl

Type in mainchat for plugin autoloading: !modplug perl -a1
